\c 232 

\s UNYIGISHE MWAMI
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Unyigishe, Mwami Unyigishe! Nzigamir’ ubugingo unyigishe! Mu nzira itunganye ngendesh’ ukwizera, mpanz’ amaso Wewe, Unyigishe!\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Mwami iyo mbabaye Unyigishe! Mu mipfunda naho Unyobore! Mw’ijoro ryijimye, umpoza kw’ijisho, nkayoborwa Nawe, ntaco ntinya\bd*\bd !\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Na Mpwemu wawe Mwami Unyigishe. Mbeho kubw’ Icubahiro Cawe, gushika ku mpera ngume muri Wewe, nshigikiwe Nawe Unyigishe!\bd*
